text: Helen Victoria Baxendale (born 7 June 1970) is an English actress. She is known for her roles as Rachel in the British comedy-drama Cold Feet (1997–2003), and Emily in the American sitcom Friends (1997–98). ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors Category:English stage actors Category:English voice actors Category:Actors from Yorkshire
